{"tid":1837441,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港續有航班往返武漢　返鄉女乘客：快去快回","createTime":"2020-01-23T15:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T16:16:22.000Z","uid":20058,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"57aed1c17f59addefeface0e121f6f391eb071d2","tid":1837441,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:37:10.000Z","msg":"湖北武漢肺炎疫情爆發，已擴散至內地多個城市，今日(22日)仍有航班由香港往返武漢，分別為早上8時40分起飛的國泰港龍KA 852，以及將於下午1時45分抵港的國泰港龍KA 853。東網記者於早上6時到達赤鱲角香港國際機場1號客運大樓，於相關航班的登記櫃枱發現不少旅客排隊登記，其中有不少乘客在候機期間戴上口罩戒備。<br />\n往武漢航班乘客李小姐指，自己為獨生女，早年由武漢下嫁來港，惟母親現時獨居當地，今次疫情嚴重令她相當擔心，於是趁過年期間返回武漢探視母親，自己亦已帶備口罩及酒精搓手液等物品作防護措施。她亦得知內地現時戒備較嚴，部分酒店及餐廳都已取消團年飯減低傳播風險，而居民出入境的體温檢測及隔離措施亦令她稍稍安心。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不過，李小姐指其丈夫及幼子原本亦已購買來回機票，惟由於擔心疫情失控，今次惟有將幼子留港由丈夫照顧，不會帶他返鄉過年，自己則「快去快回」。期間李小姐講得情緒激動，眼眶泛紅。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200122/bkn-20200122060036976-0122_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200122%2Fbkn-20200122060036976-0122_00822_001.html&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeIdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=9ea73841\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200122/bkn-20200122060036976-0122_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"98b8abb977d5cec08ab5217d19288e9671403ac7","tid":1837441,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:37:56.000Z","msg":"［行動］請文宣向有意到港醫病嘅引導佢地搵香港警署求助<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837289\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837289</a>"},{"pid":"ae6686a9e155dcb7a393f0f9796405f9a3a0d613","tid":1837441,"uid":266176,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:44:16.000Z","msg":"念在佢一片孝心就唔屌9佢<br />\n不過twitter傳中共會封足幾個月<br />\n睇怕佢都係有去無回<br />\n比D小學雞做領導就係咁既下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e116cfc41d182a85c430fa99365dc98e485e669","tid":1837441,"uid":55924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:00:15.000Z","msg":"可能7日後返黎呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e69256a81ad760111e2c0bc75072d45c2a1bd84c","tid":1837441,"uid":176768,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:11:45.000Z","msg":"屌你老母邊撚個又娶大陸閪，人地貪你有香港身份證咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要好揀唔揀揀武漢妹<br />\n唔該你快去得啦唔駛快回<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b9f2731d9a8aa3da2b65df1f1ff802f815b709e","tid":1837441,"uid":108016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2e116cfc41d182a85c430fa99365dc98e485e669","tid":1837441,"uid":55924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:00:15.000Z","msg":"可能7日後返黎呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:13:14.000Z","msg":"送條屍返嚟？"},{"pid":"2cc4474f3fb2807ecbbb27aeef6c4f81b7bb1c3d","tid":1837441,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:13:59.000Z","msg":"宜家變成有去冇回，都幾無謂"},{"pid":"a758115f7f8b831bcf19d778e3457a682ca47944","tid":1837441,"uid":266672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:15:27.000Z","msg":"快去快點<br />\n<br />\n變<br />\n<br />\n快速投胎"},{"pid":"d1632d01b7cc5bc3947879b2d2e0d5cdfd031db8","tid":1837441,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e116cfc41d182a85c430fa99365dc98e485e669","tid":1837441,"uid":55924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:00:15.000Z","msg":"可能7日後返黎呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:16:22.000Z","msg":"回魂夜？"}]}